lead_paragraph: Gael Monfils to some is a quitter but to others the enigmatic Frenchman is a bold, unconventional thinker willing to try anything to get to his first grand slam final.

headline.print_headline: Tortured Artist Monfils Searches for Grand Slam Masterpiece
